c: 2
v: 165
t: "“Pali ena mwa anthu amene akudzipangira milungu naifanizira ndi Allah. Amaikonda monga momwe akadamkondera Allah. Koma (Asilamu) amene akhulupirira amamkonda Allah koposa. Ndipo akadaona amene adzichitira zoipa pamene azikachiona chilango (akadazindikira kuti) ndithu mphamvu zonse nza Allah, ndipo ndithu Allah Ngolanga mwaukali"